{"tid":483602,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(每日一甜) 學童檢查 小姑娘驗小姑姑","createTime":"2017-11-29T09:16:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T08:30:41.000Z","uid":120847,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b4ee53a1d9d57865e7d5c1dc5ea048c4b9d07a0c","tid":483602,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:16:23.000Z","msg":"從今日起 每日會post甜故一則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗到乜寫乜<br />\n<br />\n今年form 7嘅我 已經好多年冇去學童身體檢查，直到某日中午，電話悠然響起：<br />\n<br />\n&quot;喂 請問係咪斌周恆？...呢度健康院打黎，根據記錄 你上次做身體已經係小三啦喎。你依加18歲，仲有冇包皮過長呀？&quot;<br />\n<br />\n我：&quot;屌你啦 家陣我不知幾出人頭地&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;係？咁就要驗過先知啦。好啦 你下星期六上午有冇時間呀？過黎健康院做檢查啦&quot;<br />\n<br />\n如是者 我就日劣夜劣 食飯又劣 訓教又劣<br />\n務求露出頭來，以最佳狀態見人"},{"pid":"86981c8d1c61cd91914c1a599565a0dbe6d9066a","tid":483602,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:17:39.000Z","msg":"有人想睇繼續寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be8884ae905fa4e7b38d8b66645549e9de53b83d","tid":483602,"uid":15758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:18:24.000Z","msg":"有 快啲寫埋佢"},{"pid":"e3ef6cfa63095fc1fe895d6148cbf851a2f67835","tid":483602,"uid":154196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:18:42.000Z","msg":"之後劣成點"},{"pid":"f4db7e85d1a5d3f62d4358f9c29e3e6012b394fc","tid":483602,"uid":200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:26:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51dc7201da2e2b80cd5f26b426a9d2da3ccaa570","tid":483602,"uid":35966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:26:45.000Z","msg":"重甜plx"},{"pid":"976dadfc0b018f14b5f6b2ae61190922150befa9","tid":483602,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:05:08.000Z","msg":"日劣夜劣嘅我 <br />\n有日食完lunch 我返到課室見冇人 又拎條野出黎劣<br />\n<br />\n劣劣下，枱底有個頭走出黎，嚇到我鳩都差啲縮埋。一望原來係大眾公廁姣婆欣。<br />\n<br />\n我：屌 你做乜撚野呀<br />\n<br />\n姣婆欣：你又做乜係到撚自己條野呀<br />\n<br />\n我：你理撚得我呀<br />\n<br />\n姣婆欣：估唔到你都幾大條喎但點解包住晒不見天日咁嘅？<br />\n<br />\n(呢個時候，我拎條野拍落姣婆西塊面到，一邊拍一邊講) <br />\n我：屌 你一係幫我劣 一係就走啦 姣西 <br />\n<br />\n姣婆欣：你就想呀。。。你睇你條野，就黎大過我塊面啦"},{"pid":"04236026333aa532637e29d339d105eb86c5d564","tid":483602,"uid":82829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:06:45.000Z","msg":"jm9"},{"pid":"48411c58ef52660637ef6055af5dffd610b99aa5","tid":483602,"uid":33756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />form 7  幾多年前"},{"pid":"36ad3a94d5f1978c17c890045cddf297d47a8a87","tid":483602,"uid":15362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:14:32.000Z","msg":"繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67500748ba64cd6b457eb3920a45e5d9ae7a19b","tid":483602,"uid":90787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:28:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db9db5588c7be2456e7c78a2a2e3f23516d8145","tid":483602,"uid":133873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:56:14.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"85b37f1fd0b9fbbda14b2ce062f00e7e0a1274b5","tid":483602,"uid":74479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T18:54:16.000Z","msg":"摩牙"},{"pid":"067a18c7b0e8c2aa36f0082baa7ef97306a63411","tid":483602,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T18:57:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a15964217bc8250c66bef092187da4d6abdc7294","tid":483602,"uid":27042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T19:01:14.000Z","msg":"冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj